{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/civil-service-internal-audit-profession/about","content_id":"5f5b947b-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"The internal audit profession involves providing independent assurance and advisory services to organizations, evaluating and improving the effectiveness of governance, risk management, and control processes. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Internal Audit Profession is one of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-service/about/recruitment#professions\">Civil Service Professions</a> and focuses on assessing the management of the main risks to effective public service delivery.</p>\n\n<p>The auditors base their assurance on objective assessments of the framework of governance, risk management and control.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"career-opportunities-and-professional-development\">Career opportunities and professional development</h2>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-service-internal-audit-profession\">Internal Audit Profession website</a> is the place where you can engage with your professional community and find out about the learning, qualifications and opportunities available to help you develop your skills.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Updating summary text.","public_timestamp":"2025-03-19T12:40:25Z"},{"note":"A new summary has been added.","public_timestamp":"2025-03-19T12:35:16Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2014-05-01T13:21:51Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[],"headers":[{"id":"career-opportunities-and-professional-development","level":2,"text":"Career opportunities and professional development"}],"organisation":"ec79610b-788e-46b8-b468-087e5cac3be8","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2014-05-01T15:21:51+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/civil-service-internal-au